query:
SELECT 
  CASE 
    WHEN id_paciente LIKE '2025-%' THEN '2025-XXXX (Sistema atual)'
    WHEN id_paciente LIKE '2026-%' THEN '2026-XXXX (Sistema atual)'
    ELSE 'Outro padr達o'
  END as origem,
  COUNT(*) as total,
  MIN(created_at) as primeiro,
  MAX(created_at) as ultimo
FROM pacientes 
WHERE tenant_id = 1 
  AND id_paciente NOT LIKE 'MIG-%'
GROUP BY 
  CASE 
    WHEN id_paciente LIKE '2025-%' THEN '2025-XXXX (Sistema atual)'
    WHEN id_paciente LIKE '2026-%' THEN '2026-XXXX (Sistema atual)'
    ELSE 'Outro padr達o'
  END;
